*********************************************************************************************
*** User information page : /me
*********************************************************************************************
  - accessed by clicking on avatar in menubar
  - author ?
    - no
      - button for requesting author account + explanation paragraph
        click =>
          - create author with
            - id: same id as logged user
            - status : 'applying'
            - grab displayName, firstname ... etc
    - yes
      - status (applying, admitted)
      - displayName: modifiable : pseudo as displayed on public side

*********************************************************************************************
*** Editor home : /edit
*********************************************************************************************
  - button 'new article'
  - list of articles : title, createdAt, updatedAt : sortable
    - click on row => navigate to article editor
    - infinite scroll

*********************************************************************************************
*** Editor home : /edit/article/:id
*********************************************************************************************
  - version selector:
    - list of versions : version number, comment, online/offline (readonly)
      - click on row : update edition panel
    - button 'create version'
      => create new version : clone of latest version then update edition panel
  - edition panel : initialized with latest version
    - fields :
      - status : offline, online
        - put offline => ask confirmation
        - put online => if not last version : ask confirmation
      - title
      - contents
      - link to preview
        => open new window on /article/:id/version/:versionNumber

*********************************************************************************************
*** Article page : /article/:id(/version/:versionNumber)?
*********************************************************************************************
  - if versionNumber
    - if user is authenticated and is the author of the article :
      - display article in requested version
    - else 404 (401, 403?)
  - else display article


